        Post-Sale Review: What Brisbane Sellers Wish They Had Done Differently
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Every sale produces lessons, but most sellers move on without reflecting on what they would have done differently. Here are the ten regrets that come up most often across Brisbane sales, and how to avoid them on your campaign.
      </p>
